
model random 456976

ball delete
[rmax=0.35e-3]
[rmin=rmax/1.5]
contact cmat default model linear method deform emod 1.0e6 kratio 0.1
contact cmat default property dp_nratio 0.1 fric 0.4
cmat apply

ball distribute porosity 0.7 resolution 1 ...
  box [0] [Length_XX1] [0] [Length_YY1] [0] [Length_ZZ1] ...
  bin 1 gauss radius @rmin @rmax group 'slurry' 
  
ball attribute density 3150 damp 0.1

